  "instructions": [
    "Preheat the raclette grill to 375\u00059f (190\rC).",
    "Apply a thin layer of ghee to the grill surface. ",
    "Place the Parmigiano-Reggiano on the grill and cook for 5 minutes, or until lightly browned.",
    "Add the score-fat, rose petals, and grape molasses to the grill and mix well.",
    "Sprinkle the cardamom and cinnamon over the top and continue cooking for another 2 minutes.",
    "Transfer the mixture to a serving dish and garnish with fresh parsley, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Sprinkle crushed pistachios over the top and serve with labneh cheese and honey on the side.",
    "Serve immediately and enjoy!"
